            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is in the oven, boil half a kettle</p><p>Dice the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and add the<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your<strong> spicy tomato stock</strong></p>",
